posts.post_title: WTB Bill Dahlen Boston, Mordeci Brown Cubs, & Harry Bay SGC/PSA
posts.post_content: Looking for these cards graded by SGC or PSA in any grade. I want the Bay in old mill any back for the Brown of Dahlen.  I also have over a hundred graded doubles available for trade various backs including elpg, old mill's, polar bears, cycle etc. Most are graded PSA & SGC Grade 1-6 Thank you! Many successful transactions with multiple board members happy to provide any further information.
